        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>tomato paste</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Add 5 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[7 1/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[10 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> with a pinch of<strong> sugar</strong> and stir it all together – this is your <strong>tomato sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
