    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the heated tray[s] from the oven and add your <strong>pizza bases</strong></p><p>Divide the <strong>tomato sauce</strong> between the pizza bases and spread it evenly all over them with the back of a spoon</p><p>Top with the <strong>drained sweetcorn </strong>and<strong> spicy</strong> <strong>pepper mixture</strong></p>",
