    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Sprinkle the pizzas with the <strong>grated cheese</strong>,<strong> </strong>then top with the <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>green chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 10-12 min or until the cheese has melted and the bases are crisp – these are your <strong>lighter veggie fajita</strong> <strong>pizzas</strong></p>",
