      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the pizzas are cooking, combine your <strong>chipotle paste </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)<strong> </strong>and juice of half your <strong>lime[s] </strong>in a bowl with<strong> </strong>1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> –<strong> </strong>this is your <strong>chipotle dressing</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime </strong>into wedges</p><p>Wash your <strong>lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and roughly shred</p>",
