      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>lighter veggie fajita pizzas</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>shredded lettuce </strong>to the side and drizzle over the <strong>chipotle dressing</strong></p><p>Garnish with a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
